00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:10,640
so incisively.

634
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:12,080
Genius!

635
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,440
A kindred spirit!

636
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:15,840
Alright, Zhong Fu

