00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,160
"Literary Revolution: A Tentative Proposal"

626
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:33,160
If this article is written properly,

627
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:34,960
it will be a bombshell!

628
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:37,280
Bai Sha, the younger generation will in time surpass us!

629
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:38,200
This Hu Shi

