00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:42,040
Oh Zhong Fu,

633
00:25:43,520 --> 00:25:44,400
in this time and age,

634
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:47,640
it's not easy to find a genius

635
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:49,840
who can catch your eye.

636
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:52,480
Though don't get too hung up on it.

637
00:25:52,520 --> 00:25:55,200
This guy is a doctoral student in the United States,

638
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:57,040
and a disciple of Professor Dewey.

639
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,840
As if you can grab him just by saying so.

640
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,200
This guy lives in the United States.

641
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:01,800
Whether he can even come back is an issue.

642
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,400
No, no. This I can guarantee.

664
00:26:03,560 --> 00:26:05,760
He will definitely return to China after completing his studies.

665
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,440
How can one be sure?

666
00:26:09,040 --> 00:26:10,080
This guy, Hu Shi,

667
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:12,640
is a filial son.

668
00:26:12,840 --> 00:26:14,360
Before he went abroad to study,

669
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:17,360
