00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,760
Don't work any more.

671
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,800
Go rest in the house.

672
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,120
Let me sit here for a bit.

673
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:20,800
Get some air.

